task.summary: Added TypeScript definition for table dropping.
Exposed the main module's getPool() function in TypeScript.
Fixed somewhat confusing error message when a query is executed withing a null/undefined transaction.
Updated minimum required version of sql package (the previous version had a problem with compound primary keys).
Now exports dialect() function to check which dialect is currently in use.
Changed dialect() return type from enum type to string.
